00:14:52,800 --> 00:14:56,800
Now you find this priceless jewel in your clothing.

331
00:14:56,800 --> 00:14:58,800
You exchange it for money

332
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:00,800
and change your life.

333
00:15:00,800 --> 00:15:01,800
You don't beg anymore.

334
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:03,800
We are not a beggar.

335
00:15:03,800 --> 00:15:06,800
We are actually very wealthy in our spirit.

336
00:15:06,800 --> 00:15:09,800
So use this great spirit of yours

337
00:15:09,800 --> 00:15:13,800
and use it to live a joyous and abundant life.

338
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:15,800
So that's the class for today.

